@Component("st")   this use insted of bean and ("st") is object name we want to gave 
if we not gave any name by default class name in camle case is name of
object like Student is name of class and student is name of object
like StudentName is name of class and studentName is name of object

@Value("Pankaj") is use to gave value to variables

 <context:component-scan base-package="com.springcore.stereotype"/>
 this line use in xml file to make scan all package and sub package to create bean
 of class we want 
